# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Azure OpenAI — 4 env vars required
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# All 4 are required at runtime. The scaffold ships committed defaults for
# the 2 non-sensitive ones in .replit [env], so on Replit only the 2 secrets
# below need to be provided by the consultant.
#
# On Replit: open the Secrets tool (click + in the tool tabs → search
#   "Secrets") and use "Link Account Secrets" to reuse values from your
#   Replit account-level Secrets vault. Save AZURE_OPENAI_ENDPOINT +
#   AZURE_OPENAI_API_KEY there once and link them on every remix. Never
#   committed, never copied on remix by default.
#
# Locally: copy this file to back/.env (already gitignored) and fill in ALL
#   four values (the .replit [env] defaults do not apply outside Replit).
#
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ─── Sensitive — Replit Secrets / local back/.env ─────────────────────────

# Your Azure OpenAI resource endpoint.
# Example: https://my-resource.openai.azure.com/
AZURE_OPENAI_ENDPOINT=

# API key from Azure Portal → your OpenAI resource → Keys and Endpoint.
AZURE_OPENAI_API_KEY=

# ─── Non-sensitive — shipped defaults in .replit, override if needed ──────

# Name of the deployment on your Azure resource. All get_llm() calls route
# to this single deployment regardless of the model name passed.
AZURE_OPENAI_DEPLOYMENT=gpt-5-chat

# API version your deployment supports.
AZURE_OPENAI_API_VERSION=2025-01-01-preview

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Alternative auth — DefaultAzureCredential (local dev only, not Replit)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Leave AZURE_OPENAI_API_KEY empty and run `az login` in your terminal.
# Requires Azure role: "Cognitive Services OpenAI User" on the resource.

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Azure Document Intelligence (optional — OCR for scanned PDFs)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# AZURE_DOCUMENT_INTELLIGENCE_ENDPOINT=https://your-resource.cognitiveservices.azure.com/
# FORCE_DOC_INTELLIGENCE=true
